Acting cute, making a comparison
and finding the flaws.

297
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:26,500
Hello.

298
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,420
Mr. Li. Mr. Du.

299
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:28,620
