302
00:17:31,380 --> 00:17:32,100
Yeah, pretty much.

303
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,700
Wait for me. I need to check the price.

304
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:34,900
Okay.

305
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:38,780
So expensive?

306
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:42,530
Hey,

307
00:17:43,260 --> 00:17:44,980
