320
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,500
It has a better location.

321
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:12,540
And it’s cheaper than this.

322
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:13,740
Without Mr. Li’s preference over this one,

323
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:14,700
we would have

324
