472
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:44,300
Yeah, you’re right, doctor. I…

473
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,220
He can.

474
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:46,060
It hurts so much

475
00:23:46,220 --> 00:23:47,100
